research_municipality_step.notes: Wayne Township operates under a Mayor-Council plan, a 'strong mayor' form of government. The Mayor and At-Large Council members listed reflect the results of the November 2025 general election for terms commencing in January 2026. Ward Council members' terms are based on the most recent available information for the 2025 council, with their four-year terms typically aligning with elections held in odd-numbered years.
